\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0644\u064e\u0623\u064e\u062a\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064b\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34101,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/06\/allah-loves-concessions\/","url_meta":{"origin":24076,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Rukhsa: Allah loves believers taking His concessions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah loves for you to take His concessions, just as He loves you to fulfill His edicts.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 354 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34554,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/16\/good-evil-lisan\/","url_meta":{"origin":24076,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Lisan: Greatest good or evil in a person&#8217;s speech","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Adi ibn Hatim reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe greatest propensity for good or evil in a man lies between his two lips,\u201d meaning his tongue. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 5717 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650\u0645\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32110,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/long-lives-husn-al-khuluq\/","url_meta":{"origin":24076,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Best Muslims have longest lives, good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are those with the longest lives and the most excellent character.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 484 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u